SPEL_DESC: This spell is a hack for all perks that need to use the "Apply Combat Hit Spell" to place a spell on the target you are attacking. Unhelpfully, only one instance of that perk entry point is allowed to work at the same time, making perks override each other. Therefore they must all cast this single spell, which has conditions to determine which affects to apply. Yeah...
